Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那暮羽的爸爸也是坦克驾驶员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  他是仅靠6辆MillipedeⅡ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就从被封死的Wardenburk中救出了千人以上的市民和士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个史诗级撤退战役的英雄！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而战役中光荣负伤的父亲在医院认识了当时是卫生兵的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.32,0:02:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后两人爱的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是暮羽啊  嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.33,0:02:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.69,0:02:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我当番薯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是漂亮的番薯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这多亏了彼方的照料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下就能分些给镇上的大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会儿  克劳斯也要来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.70,0:03:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也送给他一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮羽真是喜欢克劳斯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也  也不是喜欢  只是很尊敬他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨旺前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的曲子也能吹啊  不愧是梨旺前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起风了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来要下雨  我们赶快收工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:03:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃绘留？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.48,0:04:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说了  梨旺前辈很怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那号声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒呢  超帅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有点自闭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨旺前辈本来就不爱多说话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  对了  晚饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天妇罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  番薯热乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说那个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来梨旺  趁热吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青椒  大口大口的在吃哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨旺前辈她？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  无论多么小的碎片也要绝对挑出来扔在一边的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个梨旺前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  该算是个大事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是克劳斯长官吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  我的宝物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙漠之狼  创造奇迹的克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左胸是标志着第481小队团结与荣耀的狼头纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不给你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长那次结果也是我们多心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  这次可是那个梨旺前辈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷酷帅气而且美丽的梨旺前辈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  青椒肯定也已经被她克服了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮羽真是喜欢梨旺前辈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈是我憧憬的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我也一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃绘留怎么觉得？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃绘留已经睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没办法  我就借一半床给她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方  扶着她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:06:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴池的火  你忘了熄哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面坚决果断却有一点天然  这本是你的魅力所在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最近有点太过分了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在后悔挂断了父亲来的电话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作上的过失会由我来补过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.48,0:07:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但请至少在她们的面前保持一如既往的那个帅气的梨旺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是风吹的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉夜晚打扰  一级特快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收信人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1121小队  和宫梨旺曹长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐  请进屋再说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个天气今天是走不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是沙漠之狼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有说过请不要这样叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  作为歉礼我给你准备热茶和浴池如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒着台风完成任务  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很抱歉是昨晚的剩下的  但请不要客气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然克劳斯长官来了  怎么不把我叫起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真不错  冷了也很好吃  青椒也很入味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采摘和炸都是我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢噢  暮羽一定能当个好新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新的报纸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  是少佐一起带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休战协议如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商谈还无法定下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双方条件无法统一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是伊利亚公主还在的话应该就不会这样了  可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊利亚  公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道不知道吗  那个维连兰德的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲王Arcadia殿下的第一皇女哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们赫尔维西亚军队的胜利女神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和沙漠之狼克劳斯少佐齐名的  驾驶坦克的战神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮羽  那个称呼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在吗  是紧急情况！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨旺  梨旺！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.27,0:10:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由美娜那的一个孩子从早晨起没见人！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由美娜  是谁不见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞亚
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河流的水位上升了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下流的农田应该还没完成收割
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是决堤它们就全完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不熟悉这个城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你带路  暮羽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我没有看紧他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救灾也是军队的任务之一  交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河水暴涨得好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一掉进河里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定知道什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是有所头绪才出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说  塞亚在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由美娜姐姐很喜欢吃茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家凑了钱买了苗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞亚一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刮这么大的台风还来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保护茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么啊  你这个呆瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都拼了命在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己要来的  我可没说过要帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我收敛一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有父母的孩子一定要比其他孩子更懂事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是给人添麻烦  只会加深他人的歧视
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅是对你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你们的大姐姐由美娜也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:13:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮羽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是孤儿  所以明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  赶快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在磨蹭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲手养大的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会如同自己的性命一样去珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,养到这个大小就可以吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腌渍茄子味道可是一流
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞亚开始爬上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐  您先上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你先上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来殿后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好两人都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就没法爬上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况非常不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现状变得更糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有少佐在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信一定有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞错了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  您说什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  别害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在跟创造奇迹的克劳斯在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地基也坚持不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余灾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  所以我才讨厌孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不听话的孩子就要抓住关起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨旺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么可以让她们动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:16:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们一直都在看着你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我说得太过了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我想一定有办法解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯不是一个奇迹的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是那个「沙漠之狼」与「创造奇迹的克劳斯」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是恰好名字相同  外貌相近而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是暮羽第一次与他见面时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就自作主张地认定并兴奋起来了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯他不太擅长说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想找澄清的机会  但拖着拖着就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.98,0:17:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之当务之急是想想拯救那个只是长年服役的通信兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及光有热情而缺乏经验的二人组的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他们一条绳？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们上方没有立足点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边扔过去距离又太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:18:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把绳子送过去的办法…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次遇见克劳斯的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想父亲要是还在世的话一定是这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我跟别人说得好像很熟悉我父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过都是些道听途说  其实并不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.65,0:18:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为当我懂事的时候  他已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮羽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看左上方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建御雷神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉！拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.26,0:19:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃绘留  怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抛锚用线形线圈启动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标系统B7至F5部分启动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行得通
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锚缆准备发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方  动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我代替你死去的父亲好好保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:19:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命…少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备  发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮羽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮羽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把锚收回来  快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  暮羽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然得救了那我就说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所向往的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,0:21:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨过天晴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是扮演到最后了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说真的我吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你有那种能耐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看着她坚信我的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起死我更害怕破坏她的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才能做到那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底我只是个懦夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.04,0:21:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.61,0:21:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯先生很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:21:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好  小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:22:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人所见和当事人实际的感觉往往都不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向往的眼镜总会让人看不清真相
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.08,0:22:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你终有一天被人如此看待  你就会明白这份苦楚
